The '''Boneyard''' was the largest of the many piles of [[Bone/Legends|bones]] on [[Iego/Legends|Iego]]. Lying north of [[The Scatter]], the Boneyard held gigantic [[Skeleton/Legends|skeletons]] of unknown creatures. Holes in the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] surface lay beneath massive [[Rib/Legends|ribcages]], inside of which [[Maelibus|Demons]] could be heard in their subterranean dwellings.

